data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. One of the most popular floorplans in the Four Corners area, located on the highly sought-after community of Legacy Park just minutes from theme parks, shopping, restaurants, and golf courses. Boasting over 3300 sqft feet, this spacious home makes the perfect residential home for large or growing families or for investors that are looking to maximize their return in the vacation or long term rental markets. The roof was just replaced in 2022. High ceilings, 3 primary bedrooms with full en-suites, 4.5 bathrooms overall, private pool with spa, huge kitchen with granite countertops and center breakfast bar as well as a fully fenced in backyard are just some of the highlights of this light and well thought out property. Entering the property in to the large formal living and dining room you will feel a sense of space immediately with 10ft ceilings, dual aspect windows inviting natural light in to your new home along with upgraded ceramic wood look tile which creates a sense of elegance and keeps the home cool during the hot summer months. Moving through to the rear of the home you are welcomed by the open-plan kitchen with granite countertops and center breakfast bar, casual dining area and family room with patio sliding doors leading to the private pool and spa. For those with in-laws there is a primary bedroom with en-suite downstairs or maybe utilize this area as a home office. Moving upstairs you will be immediately welcomed by the huge bonus room, use this space as a play area, make it in to a home movie room or for those looking to use the home as a vacation rental you could even change this area into 2 further bedrooms its so big. The main primary bedroom with dual aspect windows, large walk in double closet and en-suite includes a garden tub for those times you just need to lay back and relax. Two more bedrooms share another bathroom and the third primary bedroom has its own en-suite. The private pool and spa has a half bath accessible from the pool deck.
